OL,3,CSex offender who abducted and abused
OL,4,Cgirl has sentence appeal rejected
OL,6,FA man who abducted a school girl in
OL,7,Fthe Scottish Borders has had a bid to
OL,8,Fcut his sentence refused.
OL,10,F54-year-old Andrew Miller, also known
OL,11,Fas Amy George, was jailed last year
OL,12,Ffor 20 years after subjecting the girl
OL,13,Fto a series of sexual assaults.
OL,15,FHis lawyers claimed that sentence was
OL,16,Fexcessive and put too much weight on
OL,17,Fhis transgender identity. Appeal
OL,18,Fjudges concluded his jail term should
OL,19,Fnot be reduced.
