OL,3,CSex offender who abducted and abused
OL,4,Cgirl has sentence appeal rejected
OL,6,FThe girl was walking home after
OL,7,Fspending time with her friends, when
OL,8,Fhe stopped in his car while dressed as
OL,9,Fa woman and offered her a lift home.
OL,11,FHe instead took her to his own home in
OL,12,Fthe Scottish Borders, where she was
OL,13,Fsubjected to 27 hours of abuse - which
OL,14,Fthe court called a "crime of extreme
OL,15,Fdepravity".
OL,17,FMiller told the girl he planned to
OL,18,Fkeep her for a week, but at other
OL,19,Ftimes told her he would "never allow
OL,20,Fher to leave".
