OL,6,FMiller also watched pornography in the
OL,7,Fpresence of the girl, who noticed he
OL,8,Fwas a man when he went to the bathroom.
OL,10,FOn the second night into her
OL,11,Fabduction, the schoolgirl was able to
OL,12,Fcontact police after Miller fell
OL,13,Fasleep.
OL,15,FMiller was handed a 28-year extended
OL,16,Fsentence last October, comprising 20
OL,17,Fyears behind bars and a further eight
OL,18,Fon licence under supervision in the
OL,19,Fcommunity.
