OL,3,CSex offender who abducted and abused
OL,4,Cgirl has sentence appeal rejected
OL,6,FIn May 2023, he pleaded guilty to
OL,7,Fcharges of abduction, sexual assault,
OL,8,Fwatching pornography in the presence
OL,9,Fof a child under the age of 13, and
OL,10,Fpossessing 242 indecent images of
OL,11,Fchildren.
OL,13,FMiller then appealed to have his
OL,14,F"excessive" sentence reduced amid
OL,15,Fclaims it put "too much weight" on his
OL,16,Ftransgender identity.
OL,18,FRepresenting Miller, advocate Victoria
OL,19,FDow previously said: "The 28-year
OL,20,Fsentence was excessive having regard
OL,21,Fto the overall circumstances.
