OL,6,F"Prior to the offence he was
OL,7,Fstruggling to cope with a number of
OL,8,Ffactors in his life. He was soothed by
OL,9,Fthe feeling of control."
OL,11,FHowever, on Wednesday, the appeal
OL,12,Fjudges took Miller's circumstances
OL,13,Finto consideration but ruled against
OL,14,Fcutting his sentence.
OL,16,FThe judges said Miller's transgender
OL,17,Fidentity and wearing female clothing
OL,18,Fwas "not a significantly aggravating
OL,19,Ffactor".
